<AuFileUpload @modelName={{"file-resource"}} @endPoint={{"/files"}} @onFinishUpload={{perform this.uploadedAttachement}} @maxFileSizeMB="1024" @multiple={{true}} />
{{#if @documentContainer.attachments}}
  <table class="au-c-meeting-chrome-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>filename</th>
        <th>filesize</th>
        <th>download</th>
        <th>delete</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{#each @documentContainer.attachments as |attachment|}}
        <tr>
          <td>{{attachment.fileResource.name}}</td>
          <td>{{attachment.fileResource.humanReadableSize}}</td>
          <td><a href={{attachment.fileResource.downloadLink}} target="_blank"><AuIcon @icon="download" @size="large" @ariaHidden={{true}} /></a></td>
          <td><AuIcon @icon="bin" @size="large" @ariaHidden={{true}} {{on "click" (perform this.deleteAttachment attachment)}}/></td>
        </tr>
      {{/each}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
{{/if}}